pageContext.claim: “Chuck Schumer sat for years during the Obama Administration and watched as China ripped off the United States. He & the Do Nothing Democrats did NOTHING as this $ carnage took place. Now, without even seeing it, he snipes at our GREAT new deal with China. Too bad Cryin’ Chuck!”
pageContext.analysis: Schumer was long a leader on Capitol Hill calling for tougher trade negotiations with China.
